<FIRST>u a AM-DNA     09-22 0382</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-DNA,0393</SECOND>
<HEAD>Virginia Court Upholds DNA Fingerprinting Evidence in Murder Trial</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: RETRANSMITTING a0813 to conform slugline to AM-News Advisory.</HEAD>
